            <div class="p-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">New York, USA</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Beyond the tourist spots - find local gems in the Big Apple.</p>
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
